comments.body: @atrox77 thanks for the update. Those new coordinates put it SW of Ridgecrest, well into Kern County. Darn...hoping for another Inyo County record. Mike (FYI @roberthansen @fundad)
@roberthansen @fundad  I updated the coordinates on this record, I'm not sure what happened originally with my details - my apologies
